<TEXT>
<P>
KUNMING, January 27 (Xinhua) -- Earthquake relief work in Mile
and Qiubei counties of southwest China's Yunnan Province has been
affected due to a sudden drop in temperatures and snow in mountain
regions.
</P>
<P>
