(AFESD) on Wednesday signed an agreement with the Tunisian
government on a loan of 84 million U.S. dollars for financing the
construction of two dams in Tunis.
</P>
<P>
In another development, a project on developing the emerging
industries in Bahrain has recently been inaugurated in the
industrial zone to the south of Had city.
</P>
