<P>
Moi said that leaders in Africa should pose and reflect whether
the struggle for independence was to be used by Africans to fight
among themselves, according to a release from the Presidential
Press Services.
</P>
<P>
A way should be found to change the current influx of arms into
the continent, adding that the proliferation of arms in the
continent has created insecurity in parts of the continent, he
said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
