<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, January 27 (Xinhua)-- Model workers are the
outstanding representatives of the proletariat and their exemplary
work is still considered important in building a market economy,
said Wei Jianxing, member of the Standing Committee of the
Political Bureau of the Chinese Communist Party Central Committee.
</P>
