necessary to ensure that the hospitality of its soil is not abused
by forces which are hostile to India-Nepal relations and indeed to
Nepal itself," he said.
</P>
<P>
After the Indian Airlines passenger jet was hijacked on
December 24, 1999 on route from Kathmandu to New Delhi, there were
reports that India was considering to send security forces to TIA
to help with security checks.
</P>
<P>
