<HEADLINE> China Opens Website on Post-doctoral Research </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHIJIAZHUANG, January 27 (Xinhua) -- China has opened an
Internet website on the country's post-doctoral research and
exchanges of scientific findings.
</P>
<P>
The site was set up by a high-tech company jointly funded by
the Beijing-based China Post-doctoral Fund and a technological
development zone in the city of Qinghuangdao in north China's
Hebei Province.
</P>
<P>
The website provides a wide range of information for post-
doctoral research, scientific developments, high-tech project
trade and exchange, scientific consultation, as well as
international scientific and technological achievements and trends.
</P>
<P>
The site covers the latest scientific and technological
research developments at nearly all post-doctoral research centers
throughout China. 
</P>
