Primakov, who once served as prime minister, met with Putin in
the Kremlin Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
He described the meeting as constructive and said that Putin
was interested in the resolution of the Duma crisis.
</P>
<P>
Primakov told reporters Wednesday that Duma regulations should
be changed to take minority interests into account. 
