state to be taken over by hoodlums.
</P>
<P>
The committee should get to the root of the crisis, he said.
</P>
<P>
Last Sunday, some House representatives asked the federal
government to ban the radical ethnic groups including the OPC and
Arewa Peoples Congress (APC), which were believed to be behind the
recent ethinic conflicts in Lagos.
</P>
<P>
The conflicts between Yorubas, Hausas and Ijaws, other two
major ethnic groups in the west African country, had killed
hundreds of people in recent months. 
