<TEXT>
<P>
BRUSSELS, January 27 (Xinhua) -- The European Union (EU) said
Thursday that it welcomes the return of constitutional and
democratic order to Guinea Bissau through the holding of free and
fair legislative and presidential elections whose results are the
expression of the will of its people.
</P>
<P>
The EU appeals to all parties in Guinea-Bissau to abide by
those results and to cooperate among themselves in order to
consolidate peace, national reconciliation and economic
development.
</P>
