elected institutions of government of the country and strongly
encourages them to act in a spirit of tolerance, in order to
strengthen democracy, the rule of law and the protection of human
rights for the benefit and prosperity of the people of Guinea-
Bissau.
</P>
<P>
In a presidency declaration, the EU reiterates that, under such
conditions, it is ready to cooperate with the new authorities and
to continue to support Guinea-Bissau in its reconstruction and
rehabilitation program. 
