<HEADLINE> Colombian Daily Marketing Manager Shot Dead </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Vargas Pabon was shot by an unidentified man when he was
leaving his home in a car to go to the newspaper installations.
The motives for the killing are not known.
